---
title: Mercer General ED — Triage Workflow with AI Plug-in Points
---
flowchart TD
    A([Patient Arrives]) --> B[Registration]
    B --> C[Nurse Triage Assessment]
    C --> D{ESI Level?}

    AI1([🤖 AI Plug-in 1 — NLP triage support]):::ai
    AI1 -. bias-audited ESI flag .-> C

    D -->|ESI 1 — Immediate| E[Resuscitation Bay]
    D -->|ESI 2-3 — Urgent| F[Acute Cubicle]
    D -->|ESI 4-5 — Non-urgent| G[Fast-Track Area]

    E --> H[Senior Physician]
    F --> I[Nurse Re-assessment]
    G --> J[Fast-Track MD]

    AI2([🤖 AI Plug-in 2 — Deterioration monitor]):::ai
    AI2 -. re-triage alert .-> G

    I --> K[Physician H and P]
    H --> L{Investigations?}
    K --> L
    J --> L

    L -->|Yes| M[Labs and Imaging]:::bottle
    L -->|No| N{Consultation?}
    M --> N

    N -->|Yes| O[Specialist Review]
    N -->|No| P{Disposition}
    O --> P

    AI3([🤖 AI Plug-in 3 — Flow prediction]):::ai
    AI3 -. bed management .-> P

    P -->|Admit| Q[Ward Admission]:::bottle
    P -->|Discharge| R[Discharge]
    P -->|Transfer| S[Transfer]

    Q & R & S --> T([Patient Exits])

    classDef ai fill:#EEEDFE,stroke:#534AB7,color:#26215C
    classDef bottle fill:#FAEEDA,stroke:#854F0B,color:#412402
